      "crohns_disease_explanation_doctor": "Have you been diagnosed with Crohn's disease or another inflammatory bowel disorder?  Enter doctor who made the diagnosis.",
      "autoimmune_disease": "Have you been diagnosed with any type of autoimmune disease (lupus, scleroderma, etc.)?",
      "autoimmune_disease_opt_1": "Yes",
