      "autoimmune_disease_explanation_diagnosis": "Have you been diagnosed with any type of autoimmune disease (lupus, scleroderma, etc.)?  Enter diagnosis if known.",
      "autoimmune_disease_explanation_date_month": "Have you been diagnosed with any type of autoimmune disease (lupus, scleroderma, etc.)?  Enter date of diagnosis.",
      "autoimmune_disease_explanation_doctor": "Have you been diagnosed with any type of autoimmune disease (lupus, scleroderma, etc.)? Enter doctor who made the diagnosis.",
      "psoriasis_family_history": "Do you have any blood relatives affected with psoriasis?",
      "psoriasis_family_history_relationship": "Do you have any blood relatives affected with psoriasis?  If yes, relationship(s)",
